data.description: ****FHA and VA Approved****Conventional Financing also accepted.   HOME FOR THE HOLIDAYS!!  This coveted condo in Smyrna is the perfect location; close to Truist Park (to include the Battery, major shopping, and highways). Recently updated with LVP flooring, fresh paint, lighting, new bathroom vanities and mirrors, and kitchen countertops, with plantation shutters in the 2 bedrooms.  All appliances stay to include new stove, dishwasher, washer and dryer, and refrigerator. There is plenty of indoor living to expand your relaxation. 2 bedrooms, 2 baths, separate dining room, and a sun room. To add to the luxury of this wonderful complex, you have 2 pools, tennis courts, and a lake. What are you waiting for? Come by (buy) today!  Please remove your shoes or use the shoe covers provided.
